<emphasis box="[474,707,1279,1304]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="39">Pyrgopsella stellula</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Rosell" box="[715,867,1279,1305]" pageId="10" pageNumber="42" refString="Rosell, N. C. (1973) On two less well-known balanids (Cirripedia Thoracica) from the Sulu Archipelago, Philippines. University of the Philippines Natural Science Research Center Technical Report, 4, 1 - 12." type="journal article" year="1973">
Rosell, 
